title: LOVE / RELATIONSHIPS — Supporting Your Partner in their Ambitions.
description: I was tempted to title this something like, "Quit NOFAP, Quit MGTOW, Quit Kidding Yourself"  —but the truth is that this video ended up with a much more positive message (about what you SHOULD do in relationships) than a negative/critical one.
